      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The photograph shows the ‘Nero’ cinema in an unknown location in Romania promoting western star Tom Mix in the films ‘Mister Groaza’ and ‘Arizona in flacari’.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The cinema seems to be small and not in prime condition. The original film title of ‘Mister Groaza’ was probably ‘Mr. Logan, U.S.A.’ (1918), and of ‘Arizona in flacari’, ‘An Arizona Wooing’. Both films starred actor Tom Mix.</ab>
